---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Welcome">
  <div class="hero">
    <img src="/logo.png" alt="Chained Echoes" class="hero-logo" />
    <p class="subtitle">An Interactive Walkthrough</p>
  </div>

  <section class="content-section" id="intro">
    <div class="story-blurb">
      <p>
        <strong>NOTE</strong>: Wrote a full guide for the newly released DLC,
        Ashes of Elrant. Click the link below to check it out!
      </p>

      <ul>
        <li>
          <a
            href="https://www.neoseeker.com/chained-echoes/Ashes_of_Elrant_Introduction"
            title="Ashes of Elrant Introduction"
            >Ashes of Elrant
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h2>Introduction</h2>

    <div class="handwritten">
      <p>
        Welcome to our Chained Echoes (2022) walkthrough and guide! With this
        guide you can expect a full walkthrough from beginning to end with
        strategies for every dungeon, every quest, every sidequest, strategies
        for every boss fight, and much more!
      </p>

      <p>
        What do you get from a combination of Final Fantasy VI, Chrono Trigger,
        Xenogears, and Secret of Mana? Yeah, you get Chained Echoes. This game
        is like a love letter to all the classic RPG masterpieces from the
        SNES/PS1 era. This game hits all the bells and whistles that makes a
        great RPG... well, great!
      </p>

      <p>
        Right from the get go this game starts like Chrono Trigger, with you in
        your bed being woken up by your mom. After that, you're on an airship
        alla FFIV (but the size and shape feels more like FFVI), then we're
        flying mechas like in Xenogears! And where does Secret of Mana come in?
        Combat and sound effects all remind me of nothing but Secret of Mana!
        I'm telling you I fell in love within the first hour!
      </p>

      <p>
        And what studio created this? Well, remember how we found it amazing
        that <strong>Thomas Happ</strong> was the sole creator of Axiom Verge? That
        fantastic Metroidvania that came out like 8 years ago? Well, one person also
        working on this game, alone. This person is none other than <strong
          >Matthias Linda</strong
        >... yep, also made by one person! Amazing!
      </p>

      <p>
        Enough of me rambling, let's get into the adventure and find out what
        happens together!
      </p>
    </div>

    <p>
      <a
        href="https://www.neoseeker.com/chained-echoes/File:Vinheim_cursive.png"
      >
        <img
          src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/f/ff/Vinheim_cursive.png/80px-Vinheim_cursive.png"
          alt="Vinheim cursive.png"
        />
      </a>
    </p>
    <h3>What this guide will offer:</h3>

    <ul>
      <li>Complete walkthrough for the game from start to finish</li>
      <li>All Boss Strategies</li>
      <li>All Side Quests</li>
      <li>Important Collectables</li>
      <li>Much, much more!</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Controls</h2>

    <table class="controls-table">
      <thead>
        <tr>
          <th>XBOX</th>
          <th>FUNCTION</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td
            ><img
              src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/8/80/VinXBA.png/23px-VinXBA.png"
              alt="XBOX A"
            /></td
          >
          <td>Use / Talk / Confirm</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td
            ><img
              src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/e/ee/VinXB.png/23px-VinXB.png"
              alt="XBOX B"
            /></td
          >
          <td>Cancel</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td
            ><img
              src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/6/65/VinXY.png/23px-VinXY.png"
              alt="XBOX Y"
            /></td
          >
          <td>Menu</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td
            ><img
              src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/d/d4/VinXX.png/23px-VinXX.png"
              alt="XBOX X"
            /></td
          >
          <td>Map</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td
            ><img
              src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/4/42/VinXRB.png/23px-VinXRB.png"
              alt="XBOX RB"
            /></td
          >
          <td>Switch Character (Battle), Call / Raise Sky Armor</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td
            ><img
              src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/9/94/VinXLB.png/23px-VinXLB.png"
              alt="XBOX LB"
            /></td
          >
          <td>Flee (Battle), Exit / Lower Sky Armor</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td
            ><img
              src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/1/19/VinXRT.png/23px-VinXRT.png"
              alt="XBOX RT"
            /></td
          >
          <td>Quest Log</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td
            ><img
              src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/6/62/VinXLT.png/23px-VinXLT.png"
              alt="XBOX LT"
            /></td
          >
          <td>Reward Board</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td
            ><img
              src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/d/d6/VinXMenu.png/23px-VinXMenu.png"
              alt="XBOX Menu"
            /></td
          >
          <td>Main Menu</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .hero {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 0;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
  }

  .hero-logo {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    max-height: 15rem; /* Large imposing logo for the hero section */
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .content-section {
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }
    .hero-logo {
      max-height: 6rem;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }

  .controls-table {
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    margin-top: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--card-bg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2));
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .controls-table th,
  .controls-table td {
    border: 1px solid var(--border-color, #444);
    padding: 0.75rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .controls-table th {
    background-color: var(--secondary-bg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4));
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    color: var(--primary-color, #f0c05a);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }

  .controls-table td img {
    vertical-align: middle;
  }
</style>
